{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2043","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"文桃路（文吉路與文桃路476巷）中央分隔島打通","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2043-1.jpeg","sequence":2043,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1DhtEvTTgu/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-18T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"文桃路文吉路與文桃路-476-巷中央分隔島打通"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文桃路（文吉路與文桃路 476 巷）中央分隔島打通"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1DhtEvTTgu/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/11/18:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"串連文青國中小與郵政公園通行動線 👣"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"宗豪於今 (2024)年 4 月會勘研議文桃路（文吉路與文桃路 476 巷）分隔島開設缺口，本路段兩側分別是「文青國中小」及「郵政公園」，現行受分隔島阻隔，未來打通後居民可以直接通行，往來更加便利。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"宗豪邀集所有單位到現場確認本案施工範圍如下："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1、中央分隔島拆除"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2、增設行穿線、行人號誌燈及行人庇護島"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3、新增無障礙斜坡道"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n4、設置號誌燈及偏心式左轉道"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n預計於今年 12 月下旬開工，工期約 2 個月。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外宗豪與黃錦芳里長一同爭取的文桃路停車格近日也劃設完成了，歡迎大家多多利用！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p